#. Tag: title
#: tutorial.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid "A Step-By-Step Tutorial"
msgstr "Korak po korak tutorijal"

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this chapter, &stage; is introduced using a simple tutorial. We shall "
"walk through the most basic steps that are involved in creating a "
"presentation, and adding some basic effects."
msgstr ""
"U ovom poglavlju, &stage; je predstavljen koristeći jednostavan tutorijal. "
"Proći ćemo kroz najjednostavnije korake koji su uključeni u kreiranje "
"prezentacije, i dodavanje nekih osnovnih efekata."

#. Tag: title
#: tutorial.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid "Start a new document"
msgstr "Započni novi dokument"

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid "When you start &stage;, the usual &calligra; startup dialog appears."
msgstr ""
"Kada pokrenete &stage;, standardni &calligra; startup dijalog se pojavljuje."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: tutorial.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <guilabel>&calligra;</guilabel> startup dialog"
msgstr "<guilabel>&calligra;</guilabel> startni dijalog"

#. Tag: phrase
#: tutorial.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &calligra; startup dialog"
msgstr "&calligra; startni dijalog"

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <guilabel>Screen</guilabel> on the left then select the template "
"labeled <guilabel>Empty</guilabel> (highlighted in blue in the screenshot "
"above) by clicking on it. You can check <guilabel>Always use this template</"
"guilabel> to make it the default template."
msgstr ""
"Odaberi <guilabel>Ekran</guilabel> sa lijeve strane i onda selektuj šablon "
"označen <guilabel>Prazan</guilabel> (istaknuto u plavom na screenshotu "
"iznad) klikom na njega. Možete označiti <guilabel>Uvijek koristite ovaj "
"šablon</guilabel> da napravite zadani template."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now click <guibutton>Use This Template</guibutton>. This brings up the slide "
"editor window, where you can view and edit the slides (and objects contained "
"in them) in your document."
msgstr ""
"Sada pritisnite <guibutton>Koristi ovaj šablon</guibutton>. Ovo dovodi "
"prozor uređivanja slajda, gdje ga možete vidjeti i uređuje slajdove (i "
"objekte sadržane u njemu) u vašem dokumentu."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At the moment, we just have one empty slide, so select the upper left slide "
"with the single text box from the <guilabel>Slide Layouts</guilabel> docker."
msgstr ""
"Trenutno, imamo samo prazne slajdove, tako da trebate selektovati gornji "
"lijevi slajd sa jednim tekstualnim okvirom iz  <guilabel>Izgledi slajda</"
"guilabel> doka."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Double-click the text box. The cursor changes to a vertical bar to show that "
"you can now type some text."
msgstr ""
"Dupli klik na tekst okvir. Krusor se mijenja u vertikalni bar da pokaže da "
"sada pišete neki tekst."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: tutorial.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The text insertion cursor</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Kursor insertovanja teksta</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: tutorial.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The text insertion cursor</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Kursor insertovanja teksta</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go ahead, type some text!"
msgstr "Nastavite, unesite neki tekst!"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: tutorial.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Adding text</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Dodavanje teksta</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: tutorial.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Adding text</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Dodavanje teksta</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click away from the text to de-select the text box when you are done typing."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite izvan teskta za deselektovanje tekstualnog okvira kada završite "
"sa pisanjem."

#. Tag: title
#: tutorial.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add a new page"
msgstr "Dodaj novu stranicu"

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Let's now add a new slide to our document. To do so, click the "
"<guimenu>Slide</guimenu> menu, and then click on <guimenuitem>Insert Slide</"
"guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Dodajmo sada novi slajd u naš dokument. Da biste to uradili, "
"kliknite<guimenu>Slajd</guimenu> meni, i onda kliknite na <guimenuitem>Ubaci "
"slajd</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now we can decide what the new slide should look like. This time, select one "
"column layout (highlighted in blue.)"
msgstr ""
"Sada možemo odlučiti kako će novi slajd izgledati. Ovog puta, selektuj "
"izgled jedne kolone (istaknuta u plavom)."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: tutorial.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Choosing a layout for the new page</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Biranje izgleda za novu stranicu</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: tutorial.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Choosing a layout for the new page</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Biranje izgleda za novu stranicu</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The new slide layout now appears in the editing window. To change between "
"pages of your presentation, you can select slides in the pane to the left "
"(highlighted in blue for this screenshot)."
msgstr ""
"Novi izgled slajda se prikazuje u prozoru za uređivanje. Da promijenite "
"između stranica vaše prezentacije, možete selektovati slakdove u oknu lijevo "
"(istaknuto u plavom za ovaj screenshot)."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The newly inserted slide has two text boxes. There is one for a title, and "
"another to contain a bulleted list of items."
msgstr ""
"Novi dodani slajd ima dva tekstuala okvira. Jedan za naslov, i drugi da "
"sadrži pobrojanu listu stavki."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: tutorial.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The new slide</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Novi slajd</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: tutorial.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The new slide</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Biranje izgleda za novu stranicu</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Double-click and type a title. Then double-click on the second text box with "
"the bullet. Type some text and end the paragraph by pressing the "
"<keycap>Enter</keycap> or <keycap>Return</keycap> key. As you type new "
"paragraphs, bullets automatically appear in front of them."
msgstr ""
"Dupli klik i unesite naziv. Onda dupli klik na drugi tekstualni okvir sa "
"kružićem. Unesite neki teskt i završite paragraf pritiskom na  "
"<keycap>Unesi</keycap> ili <keycap>Vrati</keycap> tipku. Dok pišete novi "
"paragraf, kružiči se automatski pojavljuju ispred njih."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: tutorial.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Adding text to the second slide</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Dodavanje drugog slajda</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: tutorial.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Adding text to the second slide</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Dodavanje drugog slajda</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can de-select the text box by clicking away from it."
msgstr "Možete deselektovati tesktualni okvir klikom izvan njega."

#. Tag: title
#: tutorial.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid "Insert a picture"
msgstr "Unesite sliku."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Let's go back to the first slide now. Use the list of slides on the left of "
"your screen."
msgstr ""
"Vratimo se na prvi slajd sada. Koristitie listu slajdova sa lijeve strane "
"vašeg ekrana."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this section, we'll liven our presentation up a bit by adding a nice logo "
"to the title page. To do so, the first step is to enable the <guilabel>Add "
"Shape</guilabel> docker using <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Dockers</guimenuitem></menuchoice> from the menu."
msgstr ""
"U ovom dijelu, malo ćemo oživjeti našu prezentaciju dodavanjem loga "
"naslovnoj stranici. Da bismo to uradili, prvi korak je omogućiti  "
"<guilabel>Dodaj oblik</guilabel> doker koristeći "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Postavke</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Dokovi</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> iz menija."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now select Image in the <guilabel>Add Shape</guilabel> docker and click with "
"the &LMB; where you want to place the loge in it's original size or draw a "
"rectangle with the left mouse (click the &LMB; and keep the button pressed) "
"to specify the position and size for the logo."
msgstr ""
"Sada označimo sliku u <guilabel>Dodaj oblik</guilabel> doku i klik sa &LMB; "
"gdje želite postaviti logo u originalnoj veličini ili nacrtati pravougaonik "
"sa lijevim klikom (kliknite &LMB; i držite tipku pritisnutu) da "
"specificirate poziciju i veličinu loga."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A file selection dialog appears. To learn about this or other standard &kde; "
"dialog boxes in detail, please consult the &kde; documentation. You can "
"browse by clicking on <guiicon>folder</guiicon> icons or by using the "
"<guiicon>browser</guiicon> style buttons on the toolbar. Clicking the "
"<guiicon>up arrow</guiicon> takes you up one folder level."
msgstr ""
"Dijalog za selektovanje datoteke se pojavljuje. Da biste naučili nešto o "
"ovome ili drugom standardu &kde; dijalog okvira u detalje, molim vas "
"pogledajte &kde; dokumentaciju. Možete pretražiti klikom na <guiicon>folder</"
"guiicon> ikonu ili koristeći <guiicon>preglednik</guiicon> stil tipke na "
"alatnoj traci. Klikom na <guiicon>strelica prema gore</guiicon>vas vodi gore "
"jedan nivo foldera."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select a file and click <guibutton>OK</guibutton>."
msgstr "Selektuj datoteku i pritisni <guibutton>OK</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now the image is inserted in the slide and there are selection handles "
"(little squares) visible around the border of the graphic."
msgstr ""
"Sada je slika ubačena u slajd i tu je drška (mali kvadrati) vidljivi oko "
"granice slike."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: tutorial.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The newly added image</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Nova dodana slika</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: tutorial.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The newly added image</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase><guibutton>OK</guibutton>.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:219
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Place the mouse cursor anywhere in the middle of the logo, and drag it to "
"the middle of the title page. Then use the selection handles to resize it "
"correctly."
msgstr ""
"Postavite kursor miša bilo gdje u sredinu loga, i vucite u sredinu naslovne "
"stranice. Tada koristite odabir drški za korektnu promjenu veličine."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid "That's it. Now you have a picture on the title page!"
msgstr "To je to. Sada imate sliku na naslovnoj strani!"

#. Tag: title
#: tutorial.docbook:232
#, no-c-format
msgid "Insert a &calligra; object"
msgstr "Ubacite &calligra; objekat"

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Let's insert another &calligra; object under the picture, for example a "
"chart."
msgstr "Ubacite i drugi &calligra; objekat ispod slike, na primjer graf;."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Every &calligra; supported object can be embedded in a &stage; slide. Let's "
"choose a chart from the <guilabel>Add Shape</guilabel> docker."
msgstr ""
"Svaka &calligra; podržava objekt koji može biti ugrađen u &stage; slajd. "
"Izaberimo graf iz <guilabel>Dodaj oblik</guilabel> doka."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <guilabel>Chart</guilabel> and then outline with your mouse the area "
"you want to put your chart in on the &stage; slide."
msgstr ""
"Označi <guilabel>Graf</guilabel> i ocrtajte mišem područje koje želite "
"staviti graf na &stage; slajd."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: tutorial.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Select the area where to put the chart</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Odaberite područje gdje staviti graf</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: tutorial.docbook:250
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Select the area where to put the chart</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Odaberite područje gdje staviti graf</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:254
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once you release the mouse button, a template chart is added on the slide. "
"Whenever you work in the chart, its <guilabel>Tool Options</guilabel> appear "
"in the docker."
msgstr ""
"Kada pustite tipku miša, šablon grafa je dodan na slajd. Kada god radite sa "
"grafom, njegove <guilabel>Opcije alata</guilabel> će se pojaviti u doku."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: tutorial.docbook:260
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kchart; Tool Options</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kchart; Opcije alata</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: tutorial.docbook:263
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kchart; Tool Options</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kchart; Opcije alata</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:267
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To move, resize or even delete the embedded chart switch to the "
"<guibutton>Basic shape manipulation</guibutton> tool and click anywhere "
"within the chart area. It should now appear with a green border and with a "
"small yellow square at each corner and in the middle of each edge."
msgstr ""
"Da pomjerate promjenite veličinu ili obrišete grafikon idite na "
"<guibutton>Osnovne promjene oblika</guibutton> alat i pritisnite bilo gdje u "
"području grafikona. Sada bi se trebao pojaviti sa zelenim okvirom i sa malim "
"žutim uglom u svakom uglu i na sredini svake ivice."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:272
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you move the cursor over any of the squares it should change to a double "
"headed arrow. You can resize the chart by dragging one of these squares with "
"the <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> mouse button pressed. To delete the "
"chart <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> click on one of the squares and "
"select <guimenuitem>Delete</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Ako pomjerite pokazivač preko bilo kojeg ugla trebao bi se promijeniti u "
"duplu strelicu. Možete promijeniti veličinu grafikona povlačenjem jednog od "
"ovih uglova sa pritisnutom <mousebutton>lijevom</mousebutton> tipkom miša. "
"Da obrišete grafikon pritisnite <mousebutton>desnim</mousebutton> pritiskom "
"miša na jedan od uglova i odaberete <guimenuitem>Obriši</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:277
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To move the chart move the cursor into the chart. The cursor should then "
"change to a cross, press the <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> mouse button "
"and you will be able to drag the chart to where you want it to be."
msgstr ""
"Da pomjerite grafikon pomjerite pokazivač unutar grafikona. Pokazivač bi "
"sada trebao postati križić, pritisnite <mousebutton>lijevu</mousebutton> "
"tipku miša i moći ćete da pomjerate grafikon gdje god želite."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:281
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To restore the chart to its normal appearance simply click anywhere outside "
"of the chart area."
msgstr ""
"Da vratite grafikon u normalni prikaz jednostavno pritisnite bilo gdje van "
"područja grafikona."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:283
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To change the format of the chart itself <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> "
"click twice within the chart area. The chart <guilabel>Tools Options</"
"guilabel> should appear in the docker. You can then use these tools to edit "
"the chart properties like chart type, labels, axis and data."
msgstr ""
"Da promijenite format samog grafa <mousebutton>lijevi</mousebutton> klik dva "
"puta unutar područja grafa. Graf <guilabel>Opcije alata</guilabel> bi se "
"trebao prijaviti u doku. Onda možete koristiti ove aparate za uređivanje "
"svojstava grafa kao tip grafa, oznake, osa i podaci."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click anywhere with the &LMB; outside the chart to go back to &stage; slide."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite bilo gdje sa &LMB; izvan grafa da se vratite na &stage; slajd."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:291
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A single click on the chart will allow you to drag it to change its location "
"and also to drag the borders to make it bigger as with any other &stage; "
"object. Double click on the chart to get into &kchart; mode and modify any "
"of the chart property."
msgstr ""
"Jedan klik na grad će vam dozvoliti da ga vučete i promijenite lokaciju i "
"također da vučete granice da ga učinite većim kao i sa drugim &stage; "
"objektom. Dupli klik na graf da uđete u &kchart; način rada i uredite bilo "
"koje svojstvo grafa."

#. Tag: title
#: tutorial.docbook:363
#, no-c-format
msgid "Change the color of the title text"
msgstr "Promijenite boju naslova teksta."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:365
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Let's finish by changing the color of the title text from black to blue. To "
"do so, select the title text by double-clicking the text box and select the "
"text."
msgstr ""
"Završimo mijenjajući boju naslova teksta iz crne u plavu. Da bismo to "
"uradili, selektujmo naslov teksta duplim klikom na tekstualni okvir i "
"selektujmo tekst."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:370
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open the color selector by clicking on the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"22x22-actions-format-text-color.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> icon in the Text editing Tools Options "
"(this icon has a Text Color... tooltip)."
msgstr ""
"Otvorite selektor boja klikom na <inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata "
"fileref=\"22x22-actions-format-text-color.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> ikonu u Alatnim opcijama tekstualnog "
"uređivanja (ova ikona ima boju texta... savjet)."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: tutorial.docbook:377 tutorial.docbook:385
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The color selector</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Selektor boja</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: tutorial.docbook:380 tutorial.docbook:388
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The color selector</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Selektor boja</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:389
#, no-c-format
msgid "Change the color to blue."
msgstr "Promijeni boju u plavo."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:393
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Changing the color of the selected text to blue changes its appearance. The "
"exact color that highlighted text turns depends on your system color scheme."
msgstr ""
"Mijenjanjem boje selektovanog teksta u plavo mijenja njegov izgled. Kako će "
"boja tačno ispasti zavisi od vaše sheme boja sistema."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:400
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Text color selection is also available on the <guilabel>Decorations</"
"guilabel> tab of the <guilabel>Select Font</guilabel> dialog. Open this "
"dialog with <guimenuitem>Font</guimenuitem> in the <guimenu>Format</guimenu> "
"menu or context menu."
msgstr ""
"Izbor boje teksta je također moguć u kartici <guilabel>Dekoracije</"
"guilabel>  <guilabel>Izaberi font</guilabel> dijaloga. Otvorite ovaj dijalog "
"sa <guimenuitem>Font</guimenuitem> u <guimenu>Format</guimenu> meniju ili "
"kontekstualnom meniju."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:406
#, no-c-format
msgid "Now click away from the text to de-select it."
msgstr "Sada kliknite izvan teksta da ga deselektujete."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: tutorial.docbook:412
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The finished title</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Završni naslov</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: tutorial.docbook:415
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The finished title</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Završni naslov</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:419
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now that there are two slides, why not try a slide show! To start the slide "
"show, press the <guiicon>Start Presentation</guiicon> button in the toolbar. "
"The first slide should appear on your screen."
msgstr ""
"Sada kada imamo dva slajda, zašto ne probati prezentaciju! Da biste "
"pokrenuli prezentaciju, pritisnite <guiicon>Pokreni prezentaciju</guiicon> "
"tipku na alatnoj traci. Prvi slajd bi se trebao pojaviti na vašem ekranu."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:425
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To advance from the first slide to the next, just click anywhere on the "
"screen, or use the <keycap>Page Down</keycap> key."
msgstr ""
"Za prelazak sa prvog slajda na sljedeći, samo pritisnite bilo gdje na "
"ekranu, ili koristite <keycap>Page Down</keycap> tipku."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:430
#, no-c-format
msgid "To exit the slide show, press the &Esc; key."
msgstr "Za izlaz sa prezentacije, pritisnite &Esc; tipku."
